==發行==
《腦筋急轉彎》的製作計畫最初於2011年8月在[[華特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]的官方粉絲俱樂部{{tsl|en|D23 (Disney)|D23}}年度博覽會上公開。2012年12月，{{Tsl|en|Bleeding Cool}}網站的報導指出電影的英文名稱將叫作「''The Inside Out''」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/12/02/the-next-film-from-the-director-of-up-and-monsters-inc-is-called-the-inside-out-at-least-for-now/|title=The Next Film From The Director of Up And Monsters Inc. Is Called The Inside Out – At Least For Now|last=Connelly|first=Brendon|date=December 2, 2012|newspaper=Bleeding Cool|accessdate=2013-08-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921225653/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/12/02/the-next-film-from-the-director-of-up-and-monsters-inc-is-called-the-inside-out-at-least-for-now/|archivedate=2013年9月21日}}</ref>，然而{{Tsl|en|ComingSoon.net}}於隔年2月的報導則確認最終決定的名稱為「''Inside Out''」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last=Douglas|first=Edward|title=Confirmed: Pete Docter's Next Pixar Film Called Inside Out|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=100108|accessdate=2013-08-13|website=ComingSoon.net|date=2013-02-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214220305/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=100108|archivedate=2013-12-14}}</ref>2013年4月，迪士尼於{{Tsl|en|CinemaCon}}期間在官方[[推特|推特]]帳戶正式公布本片的英文片名為「''Inside Out''」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|first=Pete|last=Hammond|title=DIsney Loves All Its Brands, But Pixar Steals Show With 'Inside Out' Debut – CinemaCon|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/disney-brands-pixar-inside-out-debut-cinemacon-1201414386/|accessdate=2015-08-13|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation}}|date=2015-04-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815231725/http://deadline.com/2015/04/disney-brands-pixar-inside-out-debut-cinemacon-1201414386/|archivedate=2015-08-15}}</ref>電影上映前，由於皮克斯的高層擔心其故事對於年輕的觀眾而言太過複雜，而舉辦一場以兒童為對象的試映會——製作團隊在此獲得了正面的回應，才得以紓除他們的憂慮。<ref name="vul">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.vulture.com/2015/06/pete-docter-pixar-inside-out.html|title=How Inside Out Director Pete Docter Went Inside the 11-Year-Old Mind|author=Lisa Miller|publisher={{tsl|en|Vulture (blog)|Vulture}}. ''[[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]]''|date=2015-06-16|accessdate=2015-06-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616230648/http://www.vulture.com/2015/06/pete-docter-pixar-inside-out.html|archivedate=2015-06-16}}</ref>

電影於2015年5月18日在[[第68屆坎城影展|第68屆坎城影展]]上以非競賽片的身分舉行首映。<ref name=LATCannes2015>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Gettell|first1=Oliver|title=Cannes 2015: Studios to drop in with 'Mad Max,' 'Inside Out'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-cannes-2015-hollywood-movies-mad-max-inside-out-20150511-story.html|accessdate=2015-05-16|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-05-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514061007/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-cannes-2015-hollywood-movies-mad-max-inside-out-20150511-story.html|archivedate=2015-05-14}}</ref>[[美國|美國]]地區則於同年的6月8日舉行首映，地點位在[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的{{link-en|埃爾卡皮坦劇院|El Capitan Theatre}}<ref name=VarietyPremiere>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Flores|first1=Terry|title=Lewis Black, John Lasseter Share Their Core Memory Islands at 'Inside Out' Premiere|url=http://variety.com/2015/scene/vpage/inside-out-disney-pixar-lewis-black-john-lasseter-1201515277/|accessdate=2015-06-09|work=Variety|date=2015-06-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609191141/http://variety.com/2015/scene/vpage/inside-out-disney-pixar-lewis-black-john-lasseter-1201515277/|archivedate=2015-06-09}}</ref>，接著又於6月19日以2D、[[3D電影|3D]]、和[[IMAX#IMAX_3D|IMAX 3D]]等形式正式在全國各影院上映。<ref name=AWNTitle2015>{{en}}{{cite news|last=Wolfe|first=Jennifer|title=Pixar's Inside Out Gets Official Announcement|url=http://www.awn.com/news/people/pixar-s-inside-out-gets-official-announcement|accessdate=2013-08-13|newspaper=Animation World Network|date=2013-04-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707204056/http://www.awn.com/news/people/pixar-s-inside-out-gets-official-announcement|archivedate=2013-07-07}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=https://www.imax.com/movies/m/inside-out-an-imax-3d-experience/ |accessdate=2015-06-17 |work=IMAX |title=Inside Out An IMAX 3D Experience |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715131123/https://www.imax.com/movies/m/inside-out-an-imax-3d-experience/ |archivedate=2015-07-15 }}</ref>本片也以[[杜比實驗室|杜比視界]]的形式在[[杜比影院|杜比影院]]中上映，這是動畫電影中的首例，也是所有迪士尼電影中繼《[[明日世界_(电影)|明日世界]]》後的第二例。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/hunger-games-pixels-everest-coming-810024|title='Hunger Games,' 'Pixels,' 'Everest' Among Upcoming Dolby Cinema Titles|author=Carolyn Giardina|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-07-22|accessdate=2015-07-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727020036/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/hunger-games-pixels-everest-coming-810024|archivedate=2015-07-27}}</ref>值得注意的是，《腦筋急轉彎》是皮克斯於2015年發行的兩部電影之一，其二則是隨後於11月25日上映的《[[恐龙当家|恐龍當家]]》——這是皮克斯首度在同一年內發行兩部[[長篇_(電影術語)|長篇電影]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Alexander|first1=Bryan|title='Inside Out' brings joy back to Pixar|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2015/06/18/pixar-inside-out-the-good-dinosaur/28879147/|work=USA Today|accessdate=2015-06-19|date=2015-06-18|quote=With ''Inside Out'' hitting theaters Friday and ''The Good Dinosaur'' expected Nov. 25, the company is releasing two films in the same year for the first time in its storied history.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619071344/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2015/06/18/pixar-inside-out-the-good-dinosaur/28879147/|archivedate=2015-06-19}}</ref>

除了[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]地區受限於影片配額外，《腦筋急轉彎》在其它地區上映時皆於正片開始前同場播映{{Tsl|en|James Ford Murphy|詹姆士·福特·墨菲}}所執導的[[動畫電影|動畫]][[短篇電影|短片]]《[[熔岩_(2014年电影)|火山戀曲]]》；該短片為一齣愛情音樂劇，其內容講述兩座熱帶火山島嶼在數百萬年間從遙遙分隔直到相遇相戀的故事。<ref name=THRLavaAnnounced>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Emery|first1=Debbie|title=Pixar's Short Film 'Lava' Announced|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pixars-short-film-lava-announced-713613|accessdate=2015-06-06|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-06-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622044858/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pixars-short-film-lava-announced-713613|archivedate=2015-06-22}}</ref>

