ayfeatures.com/inside-out-special-features-comparison-blu-ray-3d-dvd-versions-combo-pack-digital-hd-bonus-extras/|website=dvdblurayfeatures.com|accessdate=2016-03-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324202514/http://dvdblurayfeatures.com/inside-out-special-features-comparison-blu-ray-3d-dvd-versions-combo-pack-digital-hd-bonus-extras/|archivedate=2016-03-24}}</ref>

