===票房===
截至2015年10月1日，《腦筋急轉彎》在[[北美地区|北美地區]]的票房總額為3.565億美元，在世界其它國家和地區票房總額為5.01億美元，全球票房達8.574億美元，超過約1.75億美元的總預算。<ref name="BOM"/>本片成為[[2015年電影列表|2015年全球總票房收入第七高的電影]]、並在同一年的動畫電影中排名第二（僅次於《[[小小兵|小小兵]]》）<ref name="BOM2015">{{en}}{{cite web|title=2015 Yearly Box Office Results|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2015&p=.htm|website=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2016-03-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315163945/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2015&p=.htm|archivedate=2016-03-15}}</ref>，同時也是[[皮克斯动画工作室|皮克斯]]創立以來總票房收入第四高的電影（當時僅次於《[[玩具總動員3|玩具總動員3]]》以及《[[海底總動員|海底總動員]]》，後再被《[[海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒|海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒]]》超越）<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm|title=Pixar Movies at the Box Office|accessdate=2016-03-16|website=Box Office Mojo|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312030712/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm|archivedate=2016-03-12}}</ref>；此外，它也是有史以來[[最高電影票房收入列表|全球總票房收入第49名的電影]]，這在所有動畫電影中則排名第十二（以上排名未根據[[通货膨胀|通貨膨脹]]調整）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|website=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2016-05-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101103063039/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world|archivedate=2010-11-03}}</ref>[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]則估計，若考慮到所有的支出和票房收入，這部電影的淨獲利約為2.7951億美元。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/inside-out-profit-box-office-2015-pixar-disney-1201724894/|title=No. 6 'Inside Out' – 2015 Most Valuable Movie Blockbuster Tournament|author=Mike Fleming Jr|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326053651/http://deadline.com/2016/03/inside-out-profit-box-office-2015-pixar-disney-1201724894/|archivedate=2016-03-26}}</ref>

====北美地區====
《腦筋急轉彎》在[[美国|美国]]及[[加拿大|加拿大]]共3946間影院上映，其中有3100間同時播映[[3D電影|3D]]版本。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-jurassic-world-802815|title=Box-Office Preview: 'Jurassic World' Set to Devour Pixar's No. 1-Opening Record|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-06-16|accessdate=2015-06-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616215942/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-jurassic-world-802815|archivedate=2015-06-16}}</ref>它在上映前的週四夜預映中獲得370萬美元的收入——這是皮克斯所有曾舉辦週四夜預映的電影中獲得的最佳成績，然而尚不及《[[玩具總動員3|玩具總動員3]]》午夜預映所獲得的400萬美元。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/06/19/box-office-inside-out-dreams-up-3-7-million-thursday/|title=Box Office: 'Inside Out' Dreams Up Huge $3.7M Thursday, Aims For Top #2 Debut Ever|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-09-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924183418/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/06/19/box-office-inside-out-dreams-up-3-7-million-thursday/|archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref>電影在上映首日即獲得3420萬美元的票房收入，這個成績當時在皮克斯電影中則僅次於《玩具總動員3》的4110萬美元（後再被《海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒》超越）。<ref name="CS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4071|title=Friday Report: 'Inside Out' 2nd Best but Beats 'Jurassic'|author=Keith Simanton|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|date=2015-06-20|accessdate=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621012612/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4071|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref name="OP">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-inside-devours-jurassic-803802|title=Box Office: 'Inside Out' Devours 'Jurassic World' Friday With $34.2M|author1=Pamela McClintock|author2=Aaron Couch|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620170204/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-inside-devours-jurassic-803802|archivedate=2015-06-20}}</ref>接著，電影上映首個週末的票房收入約為9040萬美元，在當週排行榜上列名第二，僅次於《[[侏罗纪世界|侏儸紀世界]]》的1.066億美元<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|first=Keith|last=Simanton|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4073|title='Jurassic' Rex Records|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2015-06-24|date=2015-06-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624202447/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4073|archivedate=2015-06-24}}</ref>；雖然《腦筋急轉彎》是皮克斯首部未在上映時奪得北美票房冠軍的電影，它仍然打破《[[超人特攻隊_(電影)|超人特攻隊]]》的紀錄，成為皮克斯首週末票房收入最高的原創電影（非續集或改編自其它作品）；它也超越《[[明天過後|明天過後]]》，成為所有未在上映時拿下北美票房冠軍的電影中，首週末票房收入最高的電影<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/opennot1.htm|title=BIGGEST OPENING WEEKENDS NOT AT #1|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2015-06-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141201114506/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/opennot1.htm|archivedate=2014-12-01}}</ref>；此外，它也是所有包含非動畫片的原創電影中，首週末票房收入最高的電影，打破《[[阿凡達|阿凡達]]》7700萬美元的紀錄（後來被《[[寵物當家_(電影)|寵物當家]]》超越）。<ref name="EWBiggestOriginal">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/21/box-office-report-inside-out|title=Box office report: Inside Out scores biggest original debut ever with $91 million|author=Devan Coggan|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2015-06-21|accessdate=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621213937/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/21/box-office-report-inside-out|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref name="OPW">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-inside-hits-record-804015|title=Box Office: 'Inside Out' Hits Record $91M; 'Jurassic World' No. 1 With $102M|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-06-21|accessdate=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621211349/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-inside-hits-record-804015|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-secret-life-pets-909620|title=Box Office: 'Secret Life of Pets' Bites Off Huge $103.2M Opening|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011101939/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-secret-life-pets-909620|archivedate=2016-10-11}}</ref>

電影上映後出色的票房表現歸因於它在[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]的首映和{{Tsl|en|CinemaCon}}的媒體試映會後所獲得來自各界的良好口碑，以及影評網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上高達98%的正面評價；此外，上映的首個週末適逢[[父親節|父親節]]、以及{{Tsl|en|Fathom Events}}成功推廣的一場週二夜特別播映會等因素也為電影帶來更佳的成績。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/jurassic-world-inside-out-weekend-box-office-dope-1201448898/|title=A T-Rex-fic Weekend: 'Jurassic World', 'Inside Out' Drive Second Biggest 2015 Frame To Date With $240M|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation}}|date=2015-06-21|accessdate=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621005154/http://deadline.com/2015/06/jurassic-world-inside-out-weekend-box-office-dope-1201448898/|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/box-office-jurassic-park-bites-into-102-million-inside-out-scores-with-91-million-1201524731/|title=Box Office: 'Jurassic World' Bites Into $102 Million, 'Inside Out' Scores With $91 Million|author=Brent Lang|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation}}|date=2015-06-21|accessdate=2015-06-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621183453/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/box-office-jurassic-park-bites-into-102-million-inside-out-scores-with-91-million-1201524731/|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref>電影上映後的第二個週末票房收入為5230萬美元，跌幅約為42%，在北美票房排行榜中仍居《侏儸紀世界》之後維持第二<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4075|title='Jurassic' Holds Off Challengers|author=Keith Simanton|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|date=2015-06-28|accessdate=2015-07-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630223036/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4075|archivedate=2015-06-30}}</ref>；直到上映後的第三週，其票房收入才漸漸超越《侏儸紀世界》，並於第三個週末以2980萬美元的成績奪下當週的北美票房冠軍。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?view=7day&sortdate=2015-07-02&p=.htm|title=Daily Box Office for Thursday, July 2, 2015|accessdate=2015-07-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706195444/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?view=7day&sortdate=2015-07-02&p=.htm|archivedate=2015年7月6日}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4080&p=.htm|title='Inside' Holds Out for #1|author=Keith Simanton|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|date=2015-07-06|accessdate=2015-07-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707132722/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4080&p=.htm|archivedate=2015-07-07}}</ref>截至2015年9月4日，電影在[[IMAX|IMAX]]影院的收入為3600萬美元，約佔其北美總票房收入的10%。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/summer-box-office-2015-near-record-jurassic-world-avengers-age-of-ultron-1201514455/|title=Summer Box Office Poised To Be 2nd-Best Ever, So Why Isn't Everybody Happy?|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation}}|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906000341/http://deadline.com/2015/09/summer-box-office-2015-near-record-jurassic-world-avengers-age-of-ultron-1201514455/|archivedate=2015-09-06}}</ref>最後，《腦筋急轉彎》在北美地區共獲得3.565億美元的票房收入，此成績在皮克斯的電影中名列第三，僅次於《玩具總動員3》以及《海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒》<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm|title=BRAND: PIXAR|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2015-12-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215165524/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm|archivedate=2015-12-15}}</ref>；若只考慮北美地區的票房收入，本片在2015年度的動畫電影中排名第一、在2015年度的所有電影中排名第四<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2015&p=.htm|title=2015 DOMESTIC GROSSES|accessdate=2015-12-25|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224154812/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2015&p=.htm|archivedate=2015-12-24}}</ref>、在所有動畫電影中排名第七<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm|title=ANIMATION|accessdate=2015-12-12|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819221907/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm|archivedate=2016-08-19}}</ref>、在所有電影中則為第32名（未考慮通貨膨脹）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/domestic.htm|title=ALL-TIME DOMESTIC GROSSES|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2015-05-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67oIFDRtC?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/domestic.htm|archivedate=2012-05-20}}</ref>

