/09/terminator-genisys-hitman-agent-47-straight-outta-compton-transporter-international-box-office-results-1201516578/|archivedate=2015-09-09}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/disney-inside-out-ant-man-750-million-400-global-box-office-1201538444/|title='Inside Out' & 'Ant-Man' Reach New Global Box Office Milestones|author=Nancy Tartaglione|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation}}|date=2015-09-20|accessdate=2015-09-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bglnPmqJ?url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/disney-inside-out-ant-man-750-million-400-global-box-office-1201538444/|archivedate=2015-09-20}}</ref>它在墨西哥、[[菲律宾|菲律賓]]、[[印度|印度]]及[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]等地區則成為當地票房總額最高的迪士尼或皮克斯動畫電影。<ref name="ph-open">{{en}}{{cite web | title='Inside Out' Opens at No.1, Grosses P97.17-M in 5 Days | url=http://www.clickthecity.com/movies/a/27054/inside-out-opens-at-no1-grosses-p9717-m-in-5-days | publisher={{tsl|en|ClickTheCity.com}} | date=2015-08-24 | accessdate=2015-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923204842/http://www.clickthecity.com/movies/a/27054/inside-out-opens-at-no1-grosses-p9717-m-in-5-days | archive-date=2015-09-23 | dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，電影在俄羅斯的票房總額超越100萬元盧布；它在當地是首部創下此票房-{里}-程碑的皮克斯電影，也成為當地票房總額次高的迪士尼或皮克斯電影（僅次於《[[冰雪奇缘|冰雪奇緣]]》）。<ref name="Intl"/>

===專業評價===
《腦筋急轉彎》在評論界中受到媒體廣泛的好評。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的317篇評論文章，其中有311篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為98%、平均得分8.9（最高10分）；該網站上對本片的共識評價中寫道：「《腦筋急轉彎》創意十足、動畫豔美華麗、且帶給人們強烈的感動，它著實為皮克斯的現代經典動畫系列又添了一筆傑作。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inside_out_2015/|title=Inside Out|accessdate=2016-07-18|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Flixster}}|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723011530/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inside_out_2015/|archivedate=2016-07-23}}</ref>此外，它在該網站的動畫電影前百排行榜中取得了第一名的成績<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/top_100_animation_movies |title=Top 100 Animation Movies |accessdate=2015-12-11 |website=Rotten Tomatoes |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923072035/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/top_100_animation_movies |archivedate=2015-09-23 }}</ref>，並在所有電影的前百排行榜中列名第八（亦為該榜上排名最高的21世紀電影）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Top 100 Movies of All Time|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2016-06-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719040542/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/|archivedate=2014-07-19}}</ref>而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的48篇評論文章中，無一給出差評，平均得分94（最高100），屬於「一致讚賞」（universal acclaim）的評價。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/inside-out-2015|title=Inside Out Reviews|accessdate=2015-07-21|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709023849/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/inside-out-2015|archivedate=2015-07-09}}</ref>[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]進行的[[市場調查|市場調查]]則顯示影迷對本片的平均評價為「A」（最好A+，最差F）。<ref name="CS"/>

這部電影發行前，輿論界曾指出[[皮克斯动画工作室|皮克斯]]電影的質量每況愈下，並對[[续集|續集]]產生過度的依賴<ref name="ATLANTIC">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/06/pixars-sad-decline-in-1-chart/277155/|title=Pixar's Sad Decline—in 1 Chart|author=Christopher Orr|work=[[大西洋月刊|The Atlantic]]|date=2013-06-24|accessdate=2015-06-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617062217/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/06/pixars-sad-decline-in-1-chart/277155/|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref>；同樣地，[[梦工厂动画公司|夢工廠動畫公司]]也從2010年代開始漸走下坡，許多電影發行後的票房表現皆不如預期。種種因素使得輿論認為[[计算机动画|電腦動畫]]作為一個整體的「[[片種|電影類型]]」正不斷地「畏縮退怯」<ref name="nyt"/>，而適逢其時上映的《腦筋急轉彎》則被許多影評譽為皮克斯一次榮耀的回歸。<ref name="ct"/><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/review-why-inside-out-is-a-return-to-form-for-pixar-20150616|title=Review: Why 'Inside Out' is a Return to Form for Pixar|author=Eric Kohn|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2015-06-16|accessdate=2015-06-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617081658/http://www.indiewire.com/article/review-why-inside-out-is-a-return-to-form-for-pixar-20150616|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref><ref name="nyt15"/><ref name="atl15"/><ref name=reel>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Berardinelli|first1=James|title=Inside Out|url=http://www.reelviews.net/reelviews/inside-out|website=Reelviews|accessdate=2015-07-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629105107/http://www.reelviews.net/reelviews/inside-out|archivedate=2015-06-29}}</ref>

