/web.archive.org/web/20160205232313/http://variety.com/2015/film/in-contention/pixar-picks-up-25-annie-nominations-1201650793|archivedate=2016-02-05}}</ref>[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]則將《腦筋急轉彎》列為該年度的十大最佳電影之一。<ref name="AFI">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://blog.afi.com/here-are-the-afi-awards-2015-official-selections/|title=Here Are the AFI AWARDS 2015 Official Selections|publisher=American Film Institute|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2015-12-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702011347/http://blog.afi.com/here-are-the-afi-awards-2015-official-selections/|archivedate=2016-07-02}}</ref>

電影在[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆]][[金球獎|金球獎]]上獲得了該屆的[[金球獎最佳動畫片|最佳動畫片獎]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Winners & Nominees 2016|url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees|website=Golden Globe Awards|publisher=Hollywood Foreign Press Association|accessdate=2015-12-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708174545/http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees|archivedate=2016-07-08}}</ref>它也在應屆的[[评论家选择奖|评论家选择奖]]上獲得三項提名，並成功拿下其中的{{Tsl|en|Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Animated Feature|評論家選擇獎最佳動畫片|最佳動畫片獎}}。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Critics' Choice Movie Awards |url=http://www.criticschoice.com/movie-awards/ |website=Critics' Choice Awards |accessdate=2015-12-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CrNMCA0g?url=http://www.criticschoice.com/movie-awards/ |archivedate=2012-12-12 }}</ref>[[紐約影評人協會|紐約影評人協會]]也頒給電影2015年度的[[纽约影评人协会奖最佳动画片|最佳动画片獎]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=New York Film Critics Circle 2015 Awards|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/criticwire/new-york-film-critics-circle-2015-awards-20151202|website=Indiewire|accessdate=2015-12-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204041949/http://blogs.indiewire.com/criticwire/new-york-film-critics-circle-2015-awards-20151202|archivedate=2015-12-04}}</ref>；[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]則將它列為該年度{{Tsl|en|National Board of Review: Top Ten Films|國家評論協會：十大電影|十大電影}}之一，並頒予其{{Tsl|en|National Board of Review Award for Best Animated Film|國家評論協會最佳動畫片|最佳動畫片獎}}。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/national-board-review-2015-winners-844862 |title='Mad Max: Fury Road' Named Best Film by National Board of Review |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2015-12-01 |first=Hilary |last=Lewis |accessdate=2015-12-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203220125/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/national-board-review-2015-winners-844862 |archivedate=2015-12-03 }}</ref>電影在[[聖地牙哥影評人協會|聖地牙哥影評人協會]]以及[[洛杉磯影評人協會|洛杉磯影評人協會]]所頒發的最佳動畫片獎項中則皆敗給《[[安諾瑪麗莎|安諾瑪麗莎]]》而取得亞軍。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=LAFCA|url=http://www.lafca.net/years/2015.html|website=[[洛杉磯影評人協會|Los Angeles Film Critics Association]]|accessdate=2015-12-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151207221348/http://www.lafca.net/years/2015.html|archivedate=2015-12-07}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=2015 San Diego Film Critics Society's Award Nominations|url=http://www.sdfcs.org/2015-san-diego-film-critics-society-award-nominations/|website=[[聖地牙哥影評人協會|San Diego Film Critics Society]]|accessdate=2015-12-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411031753/http://www.sdfcs.org/2015-san-diego-film-critics-society-award-nominations/|archivedate=2016-04-11}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=2015 San Diego Film Critics Society Award Winners|url=http://www.sdfcs.org/2015-sdfcs-award-winners/|website=[[聖地牙哥影評人協會|San Diego Film Critics Society]]|accessdate=2015-12-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411031831/http://www.sdfcs.org/2015-sdfcs-award-winners/|archivedate=2016-04-11}}</ref>它還獲得了[[卫星奖|卫星奖]]中包括{{Tsl|en|Satellite Award for Best Original Screenplay|衛星獎最佳原創劇本獎|最佳原創劇本}}及{{Tsl|en|Satellite Award for Best Original Score|衛星獎最佳原創音樂獎|最佳原創音樂}}等四項提名，並成功獲頒其中的[[衛星獎最佳動畫或混和媒體電影獎|最佳動畫或混和媒體電影獎]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2015-satellite-award-nominees-announced-844739|title=Satellite Awards Nominees Unveiled|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Gregg|last=Kilday|date=2015-12-01|accessdate=2015-12-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210124001/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2015-satellite-award-nominees-announced-844739|archivedate=2015-12-10}}</ref>電影在[[英国|英国]][[伦敦|伦敦]]則獲頒[[第69届英国电影学院奖|第69届]][[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]的[[英國電影學院獎最佳動畫片|最佳動畫片獎]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/film-awards-winners-in-2016|title=EE British Academy Film Award Winners in 2016|publisher=[[BAFTA|BAFTA]]|accessdate=2016-03-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160228210030/http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/film-awards-winners-in-2016|archivedate=2016-02-28}}</ref>，同時獲得{{Tsl|en|BAFTA Award for Best Original Screenplay|英國電影電視藝術學院獎最佳原創劇本|最佳原創劇本獎}}的提名（敗於《[[驚爆焦點|驚爆焦點]]》）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/feb/14/baftas-2016-full-list-of-winners|title=Baftas 2016: full list of winners|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2016-02-14|accessdate=2016-03-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103227/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/feb/14/baftas-2016-full-list-of-winners|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>電影亦獲得[[羅伯獎|羅伯獎]]年度美國電影及[[意大利电影金像奖|意大利电影金像奖]]最佳外語片的提名；此二獎項和奥斯卡金像奖相似，皆分別由[[丹麦|丹麦]]以及[[意大利|意大利]]的國家電影學院頒發。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Årets nominerede for filmåret 2015|url=http://filmakademiet.dk/robert-prisen/arets-nominerede/|website=Danmarks Film Akademi|accessdate=2016-03-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316070122/http://filmakademiet.dk/robert-prisen/arets-nominerede/|archivedate=2016-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title='Spotlight,' 'Inside Out' Among Nominees for Italian Oscars|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/italian-oscars-spotlight-inside-nominees-877277|website=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2016-03-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330064748/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/italian-oscars-spotlight-inside-nominees-877277|archivedate=2016-03-30}}</ref>

至少有100篇影評或出版物將《腦筋急轉彎》譽為2015年度的最佳電影，它在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]及[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]所獲得的分數分別在2015年的電影中排名第二及第四。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/?year=2015|title=Top 100 Movies of 2015|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-12-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128230819/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/?year=2015|archivedate=2015-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/critics-pick-the-best-films-and-performances-of-2015-in-indiewires-annual-poll-20151214|title=Critics Pick the Best Films and Performances of 2015 in Indiewire's Annual Poll|author=Steve Greene|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2015-12-14|accessdate=2015-12-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215222649/http://www.indiewire.com/article/critics-pick-the-best-films-and-performances-of-2015-in-indiewires-annual-poll-20151214|archivedate=2015-12-15}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2015|title=Best of 2015: Film Critic Top Ten Lists|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-01-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210190401/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2015|archivedate=2015-12-10}}</ref>「CriticsTop10」的統計结果表明，本片在340篇影評的年度十佳電影清單中榜上有名，其中有27篇將其排在第一；《腦筋急轉彎》最終同《[[疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路|瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道]]》、《[[卡露的情人|因為愛你]]》、《[[驚爆焦點|驚爆焦點]]》、《[[房间_(电影)|不存在的房間]]》和《[[愛在他鄉|愛在他鄉]]》等片一起成為2015年最受稱譽的電影。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Best of 2015|url=http://criticstop10.com/|website=CriticsTop10|accessdate=2016-01-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117183034/http://criticstop10.com/|archivedate=2016-01-17}}</ref>

==後續計畫==
在2015年6月24日的一次受訪中被問及續集的可能性時，[[彼特·達克特|彼特·達克特]]表示他「目前沒有續集的點子」，卻也說道：「絕不說絕不。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last=Terrero|first=Nina|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/24/mind-blowing-success-pixars-inside-out|title=The mind-blowing success of Inside Out|date=2015-06-24|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=2016-01-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316085553/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/24/mind-blowing-success-pixars-inside-out|archivedate=2016-03-16}}</ref>2016年1月14日，達克特在《[[娱乐周刊|娛樂周刊]]》的訪問下卻改口表示可能將製作續集，而他和[[皮克斯动画工作室|皮克斯]]也會尋找續集的點子，並說道：「到時候就知道是否會想出些什麼了。對我來說，這並不是『我們喜歡它，所以就來製作下一部吧』那麼簡單。……所以我們會開發新的點子，看看會發生些什麼事。」<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last=Terrero|first=Nina|title=Pete Docter talks Inside Out Oscar nominations, possible sequel|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/14/oscars-2016-inside-out-pete-docter|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-01-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117102600/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/14/oscars-2016-inside-out-pete-docter|archivedate=2016-01-17}}</ref>然而，在2016年7月的一次訪談中，皮克斯的總裁{{Tsl|en|Jim Morris (film producer)|吉姆·莫里斯}}表示雖然有不少對續集的要求，目前該公司已將其主要資源分配給數個預計在2019年後發行的原創電影構想，而近期內將不會開發《腦筋急轉彎》或其它電影的續集。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/01/pixar-sequels-ratatouille-wall-e-inside-out | title = Pixar: No sequels for Ratatouille, WALL-E, or Inside Out anytime soon | first = Marc | last = Snetiker | date = 2016-07-01 | accessdate = 2016-07-08 | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160708180337/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/01/pixar-sequels-ratatouille-wall-e-inside-out | archivedate = 2016-07-08 }}</ref>

